(Ring) A = B + 1, B = C + 1, C = A +1

Simple Circular (Ring)
A := B + 1
B := C + 1
C := A + 1
-----
A := ((A +1) + 1) + 1
----
A := A + 3

(Big Dipper) A = B + 1, B = C + 1, C = B +1

Simple Circular (Big Dipper)
A := B + 1
B := C + 1
C := B + 1
-----
B := (B + 1) + 1
----
B := B + 2

(Bow Tie), A = B + C, C = A + 1, B = A + 1

Simple Circular (Bow Tie)
A := B +C +3
B := A +2
C := A +1
-----
A := (A + 2) + (A+1) + 3
----
A := 2A + 6

(Bow Tie Corrected), A = B + C, C = A + 1, B = A + 1

Simple Circular (Bow Tie)
BowTieCorrected
A:= B - C + 3
B:= _nine + 2
C:= _nine - 1
_nine:= 9
